title Sequence of events when user creates a new note in single page notes app

browser->server: Send POST request to the address new_note_spa after clicking 'save'
note right of server: POST contains the new note as JSON data 
with header indicating content-type is application/json.
end note
server-->browser: Server responds with statuscode 201
note left of browser: page is updated with "request payload" (i.e., the new note).

end note

